Dental Division” and struck out first sentence which read as follows: “There is a Dental Division in the Bureau of Medicine and Surgery.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/364/s593/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–364, § 593(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Dental Corps” for “Dental Division”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/364/s593/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–364, § 593(c)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “shall be defined” for “shall be so defined” and “so that all such functions are” for “that all such functions will be”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/364/s593/a/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–364, § 593(a)(3)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Dental Corps” for “Dental Division” in first sentence and “the Chief of the Dental Corps” for “that Division” in second sentence."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/364/s593/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–364, § 593(b)","children":[],"tail":", amended subsec. (d) generally. Prior to amendment, subsec. (d) read as follows: “The Dental Division shall—"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(1) establish professional standards and policies for dental practice;","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(2) conduct inspections and surveys for maintenance of such standards;","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(3) initiate and recommend action pertaining to complements, appointments, advancement, training assignment, and transfer of dental personnel; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(4) serve as the advisory agency for the Bureau on all matters relating directly to dentistry.”","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1985—